# ✈️ Airline Performance Dashboard (Power BI)

## 📌 Project Overview
This project focuses on building an **interactive Power BI dashboard** using airline performance data.  
The goal was to analyze **flight delays, cancellations, and operational efficiency** across different airlines.

---

## 🎯 Objectives
- Analyze total flights, delays, and cancellations
- Compare airline performance
- Create meaningful visual insights
- Perform data transformation using **Power Query (without DAX)**

---

## 🧰 Tools & Technologies Used
- Power BI Desktop
- Power Query (M Language)
- Data Visualization Techniques

---

## 📊 Dashboard Features

### 🔹 1. Airline-wise Total Flights
- Displays **Sum of Total Flights** per airline
- Helps identify top-performing airlines

---

### 🔹 2. Delay Analysis
- Average Carrier Delay
- Average Late Aircraft Delay
- Visualized using:
  - Bar Charts
  - Comparative visuals

---

### 🔹 3. Cancellation Analysis
- Total Cancelled Flights by Airline
- Represented using **Pie Charts**

---

### 🔹 4. KPI Comparison
- On-time performance %
- Delay metrics comparison
- Airline-wise breakdown

---

## ⚙️ Data Transformation (Power Query)

### ✅ Created Calculated Column WITHOUT DAX

Instead of using DAX, a new column was created using **Power Query (M Language)**.

